What is not a design goal of PortfolioAnalytics?

Possible Answers

GOAL    Modular constraints and objectives to add, remove, and combine multiple constraint and objective types very easily

GOAL    Support for user defined moment functions

NOT GOAL    Only support one type of solver
Correct! PortfolioAnalytics switches seamlessly through a number of solvers!



GOAL    Visualizations to build intuition about the problem and understand the feasible space of portfolios
